Davie, love your content, alwas slap like. but I was curious, do you know what people on reddit talk about you? just found this 1 year old comment:


I’ve never understood that mindset, I see great players and I want to practice harder, but I understand that not everyone thinks that way. But for real, Davie is great, but he’s far from the cream of the bass crop, a lot of his stuff is the same patterns or really gimmicky stuff like 24 string basses and all that. That’s ok, but gets boring to listen to, if you want to see a true freak on YouTube, look up “Remco’s groove lab” in a head to head bass off, I’m pretty sure he would bury Davie. Davie’s production side of things is more impressive to me, but he is a good bass player.


Here's another one:


Reminder Davie504 is an entertainer more of a bass comedian of sorts. The dude is still killer on slap but its his production that gives him that insane feel and sound. I really like his memes though.


I challange you to prove them wrong
